text: Federica Mogherini (; born 16 June 1973) is an Italian politician. She was the High Representative of the European Union for Foreign Affairs and Security Policy and Vice-President of the European Commission in the Juncker Commission from 2014 to 2019. ==Other websites== * Page in the Chamber Web Site Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:High Representatives of the Union for Foreign Affairs and Security Policy Category:Politicians from Rome
title: Federica Mogherini
